{"article_id":"MC5ulFnvqtFCPtvh","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"We ' ve removed our paywall from essential coronavirus news stories .","depth":2},{"id":1,"text":"Become a subscriber","depth":4},{"id":2,"text":"to support our journalists .","depth":4},{"id":3,"text":"Subscribe now .","depth":3},{"id":4,"text":"It ' s a stressful time","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"to work in the White House ,","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"as a small outbreak leaves contact tracers unsure of how two West Wing staffers contracted the coronavirus .","depth":6},{"id":7,"text":"Judging by his performance at Monday ' s COVID-19 press conference ,","depth":7},{"id":8,"text":"the president is taking the workplace anxiety to heart","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"- or his standard behavior toward female journalists and open biases toward Asian and Asian-American reporters just reemerged in the Rose Garden .","depth":6},{"id":10,"text":"It began","depth":6},{"id":11,"text":"when CBS News White House correspondent Weijia Jiang ,","depth":9},{"id":12,"text":"who is Chinese-American ,","depth":9},{"id":13,"text":"asked Trump about why he appears to consider individual countries ' ability","depth":11},{"id":14,"text":"to test","depth":12},{"id":15,"text":"for the coronavirus","depth":12},{"id":16,"text":"to be a \" global competition , \"","depth":10},{"id":17,"text":"even as the American capacity","depth":11},{"id":18,"text":"for testing","depth":11},{"id":19,"text":"remains inadequate .","depth":10},{"id":20,"text":"\" Well , they ' re losing their lives everywhere in the world , \"","depth":9},{"id":21,"text":"he responded .","depth":9},{"id":22,"text":"\" And maybe that ' s a question","depth":10},{"id":23,"text":"you should ask China .","depth":10},{"id":24,"text":"Don ' t ask me ,","depth":10},{"id":25,"text":"ask China that question ,","depth":11},{"id":26,"text":"okay ? \"","depth":11},{"id":27,"text":"After a tense pause , Jiang","depth":11},{"id":28,"text":"- who reports on the White House , not on foreign administrations -","depth":11},{"id":29,"text":"asked the president ,","depth":10},{"id":30,"text":"\" Sir , why are you saying that to me , specifically ? \"","depth":9},{"id":31,"text":"Trump then claimed","depth":9},{"id":32,"text":"it was an open comment for \" anybody","depth":10},{"id":33,"text":"who would ask a nasty question like that . \" .","depth":10},{"id":34,"text":"@ weijia :","depth":9},{"id":35,"text":"Why is this a global competition to you","depth":10},{"id":36,"text":"when Americans are losing their lives every day ?","depth":10},{"id":37,"text":"TRUMP :","depth":10},{"id":38,"text":"I 'm saying it to anybody","depth":11},{"id":39,"text":"who would ask a nasty question like that .","depth":11},{"id":40,"text":"pic.twitter.com/hokJOXASh8","depth":9},{"id":41,"text":"- Aaron Rupar","depth":8},{"id":42,"text":"( @ atrupar )","depth":8},{"id":43,"text":"May 11 , 2020","depth":7},{"id":44,"text":"While Jiang has yet to remark on the incident ,","depth":4},{"id":45,"text":"shortly after it aired on CNN ,","depth":5},{"id":46,"text":"media correspondent Brian Stelter said","depth":7},{"id":47,"text":"that \" it ' s racist to look at an Asian-American correspondent","depth":8},{"id":48,"text":"and say","depth":9},{"id":49,"text":"' Ask China. '","depth":9},{"id":50,"text":"It ' s part of a pattern from the president , \"","depth":7},{"id":51,"text":"which includes a 2018 incident","depth":8},{"id":52,"text":"in which he mocked a Japanese reporter","depth":9},{"id":53,"text":"and told him to \" say hello to Shinzo . \"","depth":9},{"id":54,"text":"Jiang ' s microphone was turned off","depth":7},{"id":55,"text":"as she pressed Trump on her original question ,","depth":7},{"id":56,"text":"and he moved on to the next reporter ,","depth":8},{"id":57,"text":"pointing in the direction of CNN White House correspondent Kaitlan Collins ,","depth":9},{"id":58,"text":"who attempted to ask a pair of questions .","depth":9},{"id":59,"text":"\" No , that ' s okay , \"","depth":9},{"id":60,"text":"Trump said ,","depth":9},{"id":61,"text":"hoping to move on from the reporter","depth":9},{"id":62,"text":"whom he attempted to humiliate in late April","depth":10},{"id":63,"text":"when he directed the Secret Service to move her to a seat in the back of the press briefing room .","depth":10},{"id":64,"text":"As Collins made an effort to ask the president her questions ,","depth":6},{"id":65,"text":"Trump decided to shut the presser down prematurely","depth":7},{"id":66,"text":"rather than answer .","depth":7},{"id":67,"text":"Shortly before the conflict over the seating assignment last month , Trump told Collins","depth":6},{"id":68,"text":"as she tried to engage him :","depth":6},{"id":69,"text":"\" Don ' t talk to me. \"","depth":5},{"id":70,"text":"On Monday , he showed","depth":5},{"id":71,"text":"that the threat was serious ,","depth":5},{"id":72,"text":"while revealing yet again how unserious his presidency remains .","depth":4}],"relations":[{"parent":145,"left":76,"right":144,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":76,"left":0,"right":75,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":75,"left":74,"right":3,"relation":"restatement","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":74,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":144,"left":125,"right":143,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":125,"left":115,"right":124,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":115,"left":81,"right":114,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":81,"left":78,"right":80,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":78,"left":77,"right":6,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":77,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":80,"left":79,"right":9,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":79,"left":7,"right":8,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":114,"left":97,"right":113,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{